abstract: >
  RoleRadius is an open-source full-stack recruitment portal that applies
  TF-IDF cosine similarity to intelligently match job seekers with relevant
  vacancies. Built on Django REST Framework and React 18, the system provides
  a complete recruitment workflow, including job posting, a multi-stage
  application pipeline, CV text extraction, and an AI-powered matching engine.
  The platform is delivered with 61 automated tests, Docker containerisation,
  and a GitHub Actions CI/CD pipeline.

